More detailed help is available under "help fighter" "help thief"
"help cleric" "help wizard" "help other" and "help multi-class"

The guilds are places where you can go to advance in levels and learn new
spells.  You will have to join one of these guilds, thereby sealing your fate.
Each guild represent one or more professions, ranging from cleric through
thief, mage and fighter.  Also there are undergroups of these as well as
combinations.
